{"tid":1930651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[最強文宣]中國要意粉比錢買口罩 我哋免費送口罩比意粉","createTime":"2020-03-17T16:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T12:15:25.000Z","uid":258192,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a421a5f55bfc07945c38b4b959e961f24de5c5","tid":1930651,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢招會大大增加我哋係世界同意大利社會既軟實力</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知呢到有唔少人屌意粉唔戴口罩<br />\n但依家支那比人踢爆要意大利比錢買口罩<br />\n如果香港有足夠口罩自用<br />\n我哋可以送d口罩比意粉醫護<br />\n為咗唔好比港共同支那攞光環<br />\n我哋可以用抗爭者/比較黃既權威醫生(何柏良)既名義送出去<br />\n再搵local media傳出去 <br />\n呢個reporter，Giulia Pompili信得過 佢生存既意義就係屌中共<br />\n呢次屌中共要意大利比錢買口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.flipboard.com/@IlFoglioit/ma-quali-aiuti-della-cina-contro-il-virus-tutta-roba-che-compriamo/a-QmMvWpXEQ-WjAwDvOqoKyg%3Aa%3A2437283273-5062326163%2Filfoglio.it\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.flipboard.com%2F%40IlFoglioit%2Fma-quali-aiuti-della-cina-contro-il-virus-tutta-roba-che-compriamo%2Fa-QmMvWpXEQ-WjAwDvOqoKyg%253Aa%253A2437283273-5062326163%252Filfoglio.it&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=e9707aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.flipboard.com/@IlFoglioit/ma-quali-aiuti-della-cina-contro-il-virus-tutta-roba-che-compriamo/a-QmMvWpXEQ-WjAwDvOqoKyg%3Aa%3A2437283273-5062326163%2Filfoglio.it</a><br />\n當面係習大大訪意既時候屌支那 屌到中國大使館叫佢收聲佢都唔收 之後即日再屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/journalist-03252019114547.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fenglish%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fjournalist-03252019114547.html&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=92ccd987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/journalist-03252019114547.html</a><br />\n如果何柏良隔空比到意見又幫到意大利手<br />\n香港即刻係意大利出曬名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋要光復香港就要增加軟實力打長線</span>"},{"pid":"9547bd8a1e54a9cec878fa252c53d545220b6a45","tid":1930651,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6a421a5f55bfc07945c38b4b959e961f24de5c5","tid":1930651,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢招會大大增加我哋係世界同意大利社會既軟實力</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知呢到有唔少人屌意粉唔戴口罩<br />\n但依家支那比人踢爆要意大利比錢買口罩<br />\n如果香港有足夠口罩自用<br />\n我哋可以送d口罩比意粉醫護<br />\n為咗唔好比港共同支那攞光環<br />\n我哋可以用抗爭者/比較黃既權威醫生(何柏良)既名義送出去<br />\n再搵local media傳出去 <br />\n呢個reporter，Giulia Pompili信得過 佢生存既意義就係屌中共<br />\n呢次屌中共要意大利比錢買口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.flipboard.com/@IlFoglioit/ma-quali-aiuti-della-cina-contro-il-virus-tutta-roba-che-compriamo/a-QmMvWpXEQ-WjAwDvOqoKyg%3Aa%3A2437283273-5062326163%2Filfoglio.it\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.flipboard.com%2F%40IlFoglioit%2Fma-quali-aiuti-della-cina-contro-il-virus-tutta-roba-che-compriamo%2Fa-QmMvWpXEQ-WjAwDvOqoKyg%253Aa%253A2437283273-5062326163%252Filfoglio.it&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=e9707aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.flipboard.com/@IlFoglioit/ma-quali-aiuti-della-cina-contro-il-virus-tutta-roba-che-compriamo/a-QmMvWpXEQ-WjAwDvOqoKyg%3Aa%3A2437283273-5062326163%2Filfoglio.it</a><br />\n當面係習大大訪意既時候屌支那 屌到中國大使館叫佢收聲佢都唔收 之後即日再屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/journalist-03252019114547.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fenglish%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fjournalist-03252019114547.html&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=92ccd987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.o